          "number": 1,
          "type": "choice",
          "score": 2,
          "content": "Studies show that a balanced diet can significantly _____ a person's overall health.",
          "options": {
            "A": "improve",
            "B": "worsen",
            "C": "ignore",
            "D": "delay"
          },
          "answer": "A",
          "solution": "句意：研究表明均衡饮食能显著改善人的整体健康。improve 意为“改善”，符合语境。",
          "analysis": "根据主谓逻辑选择与 health 搭配的动词。",
          "knowledge_points": [
            "grammar-tense"
          ],
          "difficulty": 1,
          "tags": [
            "词汇",
            "完形"
          ]
        },
